cs.DS, cs.AL, cs.NA, cs.CC, cs.PL 

The paper deals with the analysis of a sorting algorithm, specifically the dual pivot Quicksort. This falls under the category of data structures (cs.DS) and algorithms (cs.AL). The authors also perform numerical analysis and simulations, which could fall under numerical analysis (cs.NA) or computational complexity (cs.CC). Finally, the paper deals with the implementation of the algorithm in Java, which could fall under programming languages (cs.PL).
